nodes.label: SQL
nodes.query:
select TAB.DATA_REFERENCIA,
       TAB.QTD_DIAS_UTEIS,
       SUM(CASE WHEN A.DSC_DIA_SMN_ABV = 'SAB' THEN 0.5 
                WHEN A.DSC_DIA_SMN_ABV = 'DOM' THEN 0
                ELSE 1 
           END) AS QTD_DIAS_UTEIS_TOTAL
  from
      (select TRUNC(DAT_DIA,'MM') AS DATA_REFERENCIA,
             SUM(CASE WHEN A.DSC_DIA_SMN_ABV = 'SAB' THEN 0.5 
                      WHEN A.DSC_DIA_SMN_ABV = 'DOM' THEN 0
                      ELSE 1 
                 END) AS QTD_DIAS_UTEIS
      from DWADM.D_PERIODO A
      where A.dat_dia >= to_date('01/01/2018','dd/mm/rrrr')
        and A.dat_dia <= sysdate-1
        and a.dsc_frd like 'DIA %TIL'
      GROUP BY TRUNC(DAT_DIA,'MM')) tab,
      DWADM.D_PERIODO A
where trunc(a.dat_dia,'mm') = tab.DATA_REFERENCIA
  AND a.dsc_frd like 'DIA %TIL'
GROUP BY TAB.DATA_REFERENCIA,
         TAB.QTD_DIAS_UTEIS

nodes.label: DUP -BASE V2
nodes.query:
SELECT ANO_MES,
       ANO_MES DATA_REF,
       'Real' REVISAO,
       SEGMENTO,
       REGIONAL,
       LOCALIDADE,
       COD_IBGE,
       TECNOLOGIA,
       GRUPO_DEMANDA,
       PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
       SUM(BASE) BASE,
       SUM(BASE_ASSINATURA) BASE_ASSINATURA,
       SUM(NOVAS_ATIVACOES) NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE) MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
       SUM(CANCELAMENTOS) CANCELAMENTOS,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_SAINTE) MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
       PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

  FROM (
        SELECT /*+ parallel(r,4,4) parallel(gd,4,4) use_nl(pi r) */
         TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM') ANO_MES,
          SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEGMENTO,
          dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                    DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                           'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                           'Não Classificado',
                                           R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                    L.FLG_FNQ,
                                    L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                    L.COD_IBGE) REGIONAL,
          L.NAME LOCALIDADE,
          L.COD_IBGE,
          PRO.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_CADASTRO,
          GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC AS GRUPO_DEMANDA, 
          GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY || ' - ' || GD.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          NVL(SUM(R.QUANTITY), 0) BASE,
          0 BASE_ASSINATURA,
          0 NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
          0 MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
          0 CANCELAMENTOS,
          0 MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
          GD.DSC_LNH_NGC AS PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA, 
          T.DESCRIPTION TECNOLOGIA,
          TEC.COD_TCN_BL
          FROM DWADM.IND_BASEANALYSIS_MONTHLY_DET R, 
                DWADM.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT GD, 
                DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEG, 
                DWADM.D_PRODUCT PRO, 
                DWADM.D_LOCALITY L,
                DWADM.D_TECHNOLOGY T,
                (SELECT /*PARALLEL(CO,4,4)*/
                  CO.CONTRACT_KEY, CO.COD_TCN_BL
                   FROM DWADM.D_CONTRACT CO
                  WHERE CO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                    AND CO.SRC_SYS_NAME IN ('ALGAR CRM', 'VANTIVE')
                    AND NVL(CO.COD_TCN_BL, '-3') <> '-3') TEC
         WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
           AND R.PRODUCT_KEY = PRO.PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.LOCALITY_KEY = L.LOCALITY_KEY
           AND L.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND PRO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.TECHNOLOGY_KEY = T.TECHNOLOGY_KEY
           AND T.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.CONTRACT_KEY = TEC.CONTRACT_KEY(+)   
           AND R.POST_DATE IN
               (SELECT LAST_DAY(TRUNC(ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE('01/02/2022',
                                                         'DD/MM/RRRR'),
                                                 LEVEL - 1),
                                      'MONTH')) AS LAST_DAY_OF_MONTH
                  FROM DUAL
                CONNECT BY TRUNC(ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE('01/02/2022', 'DD/MM/RRRR'),
                                            LEVEL - 1),
                                 'MONTH') <= TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MONTH') - 1)
              
           AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
               (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227)
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN
               ('Pacote de Dados', 'Sem Projeção', 'SVA Fixo')
         GROUP BY TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM'),
                   SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                   dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                             DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                                    'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                                    'Não Classificado',
                                                    R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                             L.FLG_FNQ,
                                             L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                             L.COD_IBGE),
                   GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC,
                   GD.DSC_LNH_NGC,
                   GD.DESCRIPTION,
                   GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY,
                   L.NAME,
                   L.COD_IBGE,
                   PRO.DESCRIPTION,
                   T.DESCRIPTION,
                   TEC.COD_TCN_BL
       )
 GROUP BY ANO_MES,
          SEGMENTO,
          REGIONAL,
          LOCALIDADE,
          COD_IBGE,
          TECNOLOGIA,
          GRUPO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA




UNION ALL








select ANO_MES,
       DATA_REF,
       'Real' REVISAO,
       SEGMENTO,
       REGIONAL,
       LOCALIDADE,
       COD_IBGE,
       TECNOLOGIA,
       GRUPO_DEMANDA,
       PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
       SUM(BASE) BASE,
       SUM(BASE_ASSINATURA) BASE_ASSINATURA,
       SUM(NOVAS_ATIVACOES) NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE) MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
       SUM(CANCELAMENTOS) CANCELAMENTOS,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_SAINTE) MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
       PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

  from (
        SELECT /*+ parallel(r, 4) parallel(gd, 4) use_nl(pi r) */
         TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM') ANO_MES,
          R.POST_DATE DATA_REF,
          SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEGMENTO,
          dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                    DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                           'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                           'Não Classificado',
                                           R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                    L.FLG_FNQ,
                                    L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                    L.COD_IBGE) REGIONAL,
          L.NAME LOCALIDADE,
          L.COD_IBGE,
          PRO.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_CADASTRO,
          GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC AS GRUPO_DEMANDA, 
          GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY || ' - ' || GD.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          NVL(SUM(R.QUANTITY), 0) BASE,
          0 BASE_ASSINATURA,
          0 NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
          0 MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
          0 CANCELAMENTOS,
          0 MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
          GD.DSC_LNH_NGC AS PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA, 
          T.DESCRIPTION TECNOLOGIA,
          TEC.COD_TCN_BL
          FROM DWADM.IND_BASEANALYSIS_MONTHLY_DET R, 
                dwadm.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT GD, 
                DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEG, 
                DWADM.D_PRODUCT PRO, 
                DWADM.D_LOCALITY L,
                DWADM.D_TECHNOLOGY T,
                (SELECT CO.CONTRACT_KEY, CO.COD_TCN_BL
                   FROM DWADM.D_CONTRACT CO
                  WHERE CO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                    AND CO.SRC_SYS_NAME IN ('ALGAR CRM', 'VANTIVE')
                    AND NVL(CO.COD_TCN_BL, '-3') <> '-3') TEC
        
         WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
           AND R.PRODUCT_KEY = PRO.PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.LOCALITY_KEY = L.LOCALITY_KEY
           AND L.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND PRO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.TECHNOLOGY_KEY = T.TECHNOLOGY_KEY
           AND T.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.CONTRACT_KEY = TEC.CONTRACT_KEY(+)
           AND R.POST_DATE =
               (select trunc(max(post_date))
                  FROM DWADM.IND_BASEANALYSIS_MONTHLY_DET DD,
                       dwadm.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT             GG
                 where GG.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = DD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
                   AND GG.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                   AND (DD.POST_DATE = to_date(sysdate - 1) and
                       DD.POST_DATE <> LAST_DAY(TRUNC(SYSDATE - 1, 'mm')))
                   AND GG.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
                       (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227)
                   AND GG.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL)
           AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
               (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227)
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN
               ('Pacote de Dados', 'Sem Projeção', 'SVA Fixo')
         GROUP BY R.POST_DATE,
                   SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                   TO_CHAR(R.POST_DATE,
                           'DD-MON-YYYY',
                           'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=PORTUGUESE'),
                   dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                             DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                                    'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                                    'Não Classificado',
                                                    R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                             L.FLG_FNQ,
                                             L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                             L.COD_IBGE),
                   GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC,
                   GD.DESCRIPTION,
                   GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY,
                   L.NAME,
                   L.COD_IBGE,
                   PRO.DESCRIPTION,
                   GD.DSC_LNH_NGC, 
                   T.DESCRIPTION,
                   TEC.COD_TCN_BL)
 GROUP BY ANO_MES,
          DATA_REF,
          SEGMENTO,
          REGIONAL,
          LOCALIDADE,
          COD_IBGE,
          TECNOLOGIA,
          GRUPO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

SELECT ANO_MES,

       SUM(MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE) MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
       SUM(CANCELAMENTOS) CANCELAMENTOS,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_SAINTE) MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
       PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

  FROM (
        SELECT /*+ parallel(r, 4) parallel(gd, 4) use_nl(pi r) */
         TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM') ANO_MES,
         seg.customer_segment SEGMENTO,
         dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                   DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                          'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                          'Não Classificado',
                                          R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                   L.FLG_FNQ,
                                   L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                   L.COD_IBGE) REGIONAL,
         L.NAME LOCALIDADE,
         L.COD_IBGE,
         P.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_CADASTRO,
         GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC AS GRUPO_DEMANDA, 
         GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY || ' - ' || GD.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
         0 BASE,
         0 BASE_ASSINATURA,
         CASE
           WHEN r.activation_type = 'NOVA ATIVAÇÃO' THEN
            NVL(SUM(R.Quantity), 0)
           ELSE
            0
         END NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
         CASE
           WHEN r.activation_type = 'MIGRAÇÃO' THEN
            NVL(SUM(R.Quantity), 0)
           ELSE
            0
         END MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
         0 CANCELAMENTOS,
         0 MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
         GD.DSC_LNH_NGC AS PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA, 
         T.DESCRIPTION TECNOLOGIA,
         TEC.COD_TCN_BL
          FROM DWADM.IND_NEWACTIVATIONS_DAILY_DET R,
               DWADM.D_PRODUCT P,
               DWADM.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT GD,
               DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEG,
               DWADM.D_LOCALITY L,
               DWADM.D_TECHNOLOGY T,
               (SELECT CO.CONTRACT_KEY, CO.COD_TCN_BL
                  FROM DWADM.D_CONTRACT CO
                 WHERE CO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                   AND CO.SRC_SYS_NAME IN ('ALGAR CRM', 'VANTIVE')
                   AND NVL(CO.COD_TCN_BL, '-3') <> '-3') TEC
         WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
           AND P.PRODUCT_KEY = R.PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.LOCALITY_KEY = L.LOCALITY_KEY
           AND L.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS||null = 1
           AND P.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.TECHNOLOGY_KEY = T.TECHNOLOGY_KEY
           AND T.RECORD_STATUS||null = 1
           AND R.CONTRACT_KEY = TEC.CONTRACT_KEY(+)
           AND R.POST_DATE >= TO_DATE('01/02/2022', 'DD/MM/YYYY') 
           AND R.POST_DATE <= LAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE(SYSDATE), -1))
           AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
               (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 215, 216, 214, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227)
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN
               ('Pacote de Dados', 'Sem Projeção', 'SVA Fixo')
        
        
        
         GROUP BY TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM'),
                  SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                  dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                            DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                                   'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                                   'Não Classificado',
                                                   R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                            L.FLG_FNQ,
                                            L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                            L.COD_IBGE),
                  GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC,
                  GD.DESCRIPTION,
                  GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY,
                  R.ACTIVATION_TYPE,
                  L.NAME,
                  L.COD_IBGE,
                  P.DESCRIPTION,
                  GD.DSC_LNH_NGC, 
                  T.DESCRIPTION,
                  TEC.COD_TCN_BL
       )
 GROUP BY ANO_MES,
          SEGMENTO,
          REGIONAL,
          LOCALIDADE,
          COD_IBGE,
          TECNOLOGIA,
          GRUPO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

UNION ALL

nodes.label: BASE V2
nodes.query:
SELECT ANO_MES,
       ANO_MES DATA_REF,
       'Real' REVISAO,
       SEGMENTO,
       REGIONAL,
       LOCALIDADE,
       COD_IBGE,
       TECNOLOGIA,
       GRUPO_DEMANDA,
       PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
       SUM(BASE) BASE,
       SUM(BASE_ASSINATURA) BASE_ASSINATURA,
       SUM(NOVAS_ATIVACOES) NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE) MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
       SUM(CANCELAMENTOS) CANCELAMENTOS,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_SAINTE) MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
       PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

  FROM (
        SELECT /*+ parallel(r,4,4) parallel(gd,4,4) use_nl(pi r) */
         TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM') ANO_MES,
          SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEGMENTO,

                                    DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                           'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                           'Não Classificado',
                                           R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                    L.FLG_FNQ,
                                    L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                    L.COD_IBGE) REGIONAL,
          L.NAME LOCALIDADE,
          L.COD_IBGE,
          PRO.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_CADASTRO,
          GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC AS GRUPO_DEMANDA, 
          GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY || ' - ' || GD.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          NVL(SUM(R.QUANTITY), 0) BASE,
          0 BASE_ASSINATURA,
          0 NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
          0 MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
          0 CANCELAMENTOS,
          0 MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
          GD.DSC_LNH_NGC AS PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA, 
          T.DESCRIPTION TECNOLOGIA,
          TEC.COD_TCN_BL
          FROM DWADM.IND_BASEANALYSIS_MONTHLY_DET R, 
                DWADM.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT GD, 
                DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEG, 
                DWADM.D_PRODUCT PRO, 
                DWADM.D_LOCALITY L,
                DWADM.D_TECHNOLOGY T,
                (SELECT /*PARALLEL(CO,4,4)*/
                  CO.CONTRACT_KEY, CO.COD_TCN_BL
                   FROM DWADM.D_CONTRACT CO
                  WHERE CO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                    AND CO.SRC_SYS_NAME IN ('ALGAR CRM', 'VANTIVE')
                    AND NVL(CO.COD_TCN_BL, '-3') <> '-3') TEC
         WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
           AND R.PRODUCT_KEY = PRO.PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.LOCALITY_KEY = L.LOCALITY_KEY
           AND L.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND PRO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.TECHNOLOGY_KEY = T.TECHNOLOGY_KEY
           AND T.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.CONTRACT_KEY = TEC.CONTRACT_KEY(+)   
           AND R.POST_DATE IN
               (SELECT LAST_DAY(TRUNC(ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE('01/02/2022',
                                                         'DD/MM/RRRR'),
                                                 LEVEL - 1),
                                      'MONTH')) AS LAST_DAY_OF_MONTH
                  FROM DUAL
                CONNECT BY TRUNC(ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE('01/02/2022', 'DD/MM/RRRR'),
                                            LEVEL - 1),
                                 'MONTH') <= TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MONTH') - 1)
              
           AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
               (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227, 231, 232, 233)
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN
               ('Pacote de Dados', 'Sem Projeção', 'SVA Fixo')
         GROUP BY TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM'),
                   SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                   dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                             DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                                    'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                                    'Não Classificado',
                                                    R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                             L.FLG_FNQ,
                                             L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                             L.COD_IBGE),
                   GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC,
                   GD.DSC_LNH_NGC,
                   GD.DESCRIPTION,
                   GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY,
                   L.NAME,
                   L.COD_IBGE,
                   PRO.DESCRIPTION,
                   T.DESCRIPTION,
                   TEC.COD_TCN_BL
       )
 GROUP BY ANO_MES,
          SEGMENTO,
          REGIONAL,
          LOCALIDADE,
          COD_IBGE,
          TECNOLOGIA,
          GRUPO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA
UNION ALL

select ANO_MES,
       DATA_REF,
       'Real' REVISAO,
       SEGMENTO,
       REGIONAL,
       LOCALIDADE,
       COD_IBGE,
       TECNOLOGIA,
       GRUPO_DEMANDA,
       PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
       SUM(BASE) BASE,
       SUM(BASE_ASSINATURA) BASE_ASSINATURA,
       SUM(NOVAS_ATIVACOES) NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE) MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
       SUM(CANCELAMENTOS) CANCELAMENTOS,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_SAINTE) MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
       PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

  from (
        SELECT /*+ parallel(r, 4) parallel(gd, 4) use_nl(pi r) */
         TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM') ANO_MES,
          R.POST_DATE DATA_REF,
          SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEGMENTO,
          dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                    DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                           'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                           'Não Classificado',
                                           R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                    L.FLG_FNQ,
                                    L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                    L.COD_IBGE) REGIONAL,
          L.NAME LOCALIDADE,
          L.COD_IBGE,
          PRO.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_CADASTRO,
          GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC AS GRUPO_DEMANDA, 
          GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY || ' - ' || GD.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          NVL(SUM(R.QUANTITY), 0) BASE,
          0 BASE_ASSINATURA,
          0 NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
          0 MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
          0 CANCELAMENTOS,
          0 MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
          GD.DSC_LNH_NGC AS PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA, 
          T.DESCRIPTION TECNOLOGIA,
          TEC.COD_TCN_BL
          FROM DWADM.IND_BASEANALYSIS_MONTHLY_DET R, 
                dwadm.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT GD, 
                DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEG, 
                DWADM.D_PRODUCT PRO, 
                DWADM.D_LOCALITY L,
                DWADM.D_TECHNOLOGY T,
                (SELECT CO.CONTRACT_KEY, CO.COD_TCN_BL
                   FROM DWADM.D_CONTRACT CO
                  WHERE CO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                    AND CO.SRC_SYS_NAME IN ('ALGAR CRM', 'VANTIVE')
                    AND NVL(CO.COD_TCN_BL, '-3') <> '-3') TEC
        
         WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
           AND R.PRODUCT_KEY = PRO.PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.LOCALITY_KEY = L.LOCALITY_KEY
           AND L.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND PRO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.TECHNOLOGY_KEY = T.TECHNOLOGY_KEY
           AND T.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND R.CONTRACT_KEY = TEC.CONTRACT_KEY(+)
           AND R.POST_DATE =
               (select trunc(max(post_date))
                  FROM DWADM.IND_BASEANALYSIS_MONTHLY_DET DD,
                       dwadm.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT             GG
                 where GG.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = DD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
                   AND GG.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                   AND (DD.POST_DATE = to_date(sysdate - 1) and
                       DD.POST_DATE <> LAST_DAY(TRUNC(SYSDATE - 1, 'mm')))
                   AND GG.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
                       (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227, 231, 232, 233)
                   AND GG.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL)
           AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
               (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227, 231, 232, 233)
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN
               ('Pacote de Dados', 'Sem Projeção', 'SVA Fixo')
         GROUP BY R.POST_DATE,
                   SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                   TO_CHAR(R.POST_DATE,
                           'DD-MON-YYYY',
                           'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=PORTUGUESE'),
                   dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                             DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                                    'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                                    'Não Classificado',
                                                    R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                             L.FLG_FNQ,
                                             L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                             L.COD_IBGE),
                   GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC,
                   GD.DESCRIPTION,
                   GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY,
                   L.NAME,
                   L.COD_IBGE,
                   PRO.DESCRIPTION,
                   GD.DSC_LNH_NGC, 
                   T.DESCRIPTION,
                   TEC.COD_TCN_BL)
 GROUP BY ANO_MES,
          DATA_REF,
          SEGMENTO,
          REGIONAL,
          LOCALIDADE,
          COD_IBGE,
          TECNOLOGIA,
          GRUPO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

nodes.label: CANCELAMENTOS
nodes.query:
SELECT ANO_MES,
       ANO_MES DATA_REF,
       'Real' REVISAO,
       SEGMENTO,
       REGIONAL,
       LOCALIDADE,
       COD_IBGE,
       TECNOLOGIA,
       GRUPO_DEMANDA,
       PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
       SUM(BASE) BASE,
       SUM(BASE_ASSINATURA) BASE_ASSINATURA,
       SUM(NOVAS_ATIVACOES) NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE) MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
       SUM(CANCELAMENTOS) CANCELAMENTOS,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_SAINTE) MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
       PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

  FROM (
        SELECT /*+ parallel(r, 4) parallel(gd, 4) use_nl(pi r) */
         TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM') ANO_MES,
         SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEGMENTO,
         dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                   DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                          'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                          'Não Classificado',
                                          R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                   L.FLG_FNQ,
                                   L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                   L.COD_IBGE) REGIONAL,
         L.NAME LOCALIDADE,
         L.COD_IBGE,
         P.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_CADASTRO,
         GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC AS GRUPO_DEMANDA, 
         GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY || ' - ' || GD.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
         0 BASE,
         0 BASE_ASSINATURA,
         0 NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
         0 MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
         CASE
           WHEN r.cancellation_type = 'CANCELAMENTO' THEN
            NVL(SUM(R.Quantity), 0)
           ELSE
            0
         END CANCELAMENTOS,
         CASE
           WHEN r.cancellation_type = 'MIGRAÇÃO' THEN
            NVL(SUM(R.Quantity), 0)
           ELSE
            0
         END MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
         GD.DSC_LNH_NGC AS PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA, 
         T.DESCRIPTION TECNOLOGIA,
         TEC.COD_TCN_BL
          FROM DWADM.IND_CHURN_DAILY_DET R,
               DWADM.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT GD,
               DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEG,
               DWADM.D_PRODUCT P,
               DWADM.D_LOCALITY L,
               DWADM.D_TECHNOLOGY T,
               (SELECT CO.CONTRACT_KEY, CO.COD_TCN_BL
                  FROM DWADM.D_CONTRACT CO
                 WHERE CO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                   AND CO.SRC_SYS_NAME IN ('ALGAR CRM', 'VANTIVE')
                   AND NVL(CO.COD_TCN_BL, '-3') <> '-3') TEC
         WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
           AND P.PRODUCT_KEY = R.PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.LOCALITY_KEY = L.LOCALITY_KEY
           AND L.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND P.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS||null = 1
           AND R.TECHNOLOGY_KEY = T.TECHNOLOGY_KEY
           AND T.RECORD_STATUS||null = 1
           AND R.CONTRACT_KEY = TEC.CONTRACT_KEY(+)
           AND R.POST_DATE >= TO_DATE('01/02/2022', 'DD/MM/YYYY') 
           AND R.POST_DATE <= LAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE(SYSDATE), -1))
           AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
               (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227)
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN
               ('Pacote de Dados', 'Sem Projeção', 'SVA Fixo')
        
         GROUP BY TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM'),
                  L.COD_IBGE,
                  SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                  P.DESCRIPTION,
                  GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC,
                  GD.DESCRIPTION,
                  GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY,
                  dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                            DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                                   'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                                   'Não Classificado',
                                                   R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                            L.FLG_FNQ,
                                            L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                            L.COD_IBGE),
                  R.CANCELLATION_TYPE,
                  L.NAME,
                  GD.DSC_LNH_NGC, 
                  T.DESCRIPTION,
                  TEC.COD_TCN_BL)
 GROUP BY ANO_MES,
          SEGMENTO,
          REGIONAL,
          LOCALIDADE,
          COD_IBGE,
          TECNOLOGIA,
          GRUPO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

UNION ALL

select ANO_MES,
       DATA_REF,
       'Real' REVISAO,
       SEGMENTO,
       REGIONAL,
       LOCALIDADE,
       COD_IBGE,
       TECNOLOGIA,
       GRUPO_DEMANDA,
       PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
       SUM(BASE) BASE,
       SUM(BASE_ASSINATURA) BASE_ASSINATURA,
       SUM(NOVAS_ATIVACOES) NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE) MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
       SUM(CANCELAMENTOS) CANCELAMENTOS,
       SUM(MIGRACAO_SAINTE) MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
       PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

  from (
        SELECT /*+ parallel(r, 4) parallel(gd, 4) use_nl(pi r) */
         TRUNC(R.POST_DATE, 'MM') ANO_MES,
         R.POST_DATE DATA_REF,
         SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEGMENTO,
         dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                   DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                          'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                          'Não Classificado',
                                          R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                   L.FLG_FNQ,
                                   L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                   L.COD_IBGE) REGIONAL,
         
         L.NAME LOCALIDADE,
         L.COD_IBGE,
         P.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_CADASTRO,
         GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC AS GRUPO_DEMANDA, 
         GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY || ' - ' || GD.DESCRIPTION PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
         0 BASE,
         0 BASE_ASSINATURA,
         0 NOVAS_ATIVACOES,
         0 MIGRACAO_ENTRANTE,
         CASE
           WHEN R.CANCELLATION_TYPE = 'CANCELAMENTO' THEN
            NVL(SUM(R.QUANTITY), 0)
           ELSE
            0
         END CANCELAMENTOS,
         CASE
           WHEN R.CANCELLATION_TYPE = 'MIGRAÇÃO' THEN
            NVL(SUM(R.QUANTITY), 0)
           ELSE
            0
         END MIGRACAO_SAINTE,
         GD.DSC_LNH_NGC AS PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA, 
         T.DESCRIPTION TECNOLOGIA,
         TEC.COD_TCN_BL
          FROM DWADM.IND_CHURN_DAILY_DET R,
               dwadm.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT GD,
               DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT SEG,
               DWADM.D_PRODUCT P,
               DWADM.D_LOCALITY L,
               DWADM.D_TECHNOLOGY T,
               (SELECT CO.CONTRACT_KEY, CO.COD_TCN_BL
                  FROM DWADM.D_CONTRACT CO
                 WHERE CO.RECORD_STATUS = 1
                   AND CO.SRC_SYS_NAME IN ('ALGAR CRM', 'VANTIVE')
                   AND NVL(CO.COD_TCN_BL, '-3') <> '-3') TEC
         WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
           AND P.PRODUCT_KEY = R.PRODUCT_KEY
           AND R.LOCALITY_KEY = L.LOCALITY_KEY
           AND L.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND P.RECORD_STATUS = 1
           AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS||null = 1
           AND R.TECHNOLOGY_KEY = T.TECHNOLOGY_KEY
           AND T.RECORD_STATUS||null = 1
           AND R.CONTRACT_KEY = TEC.CONTRACT_KEY(+)
              
              
              
              
              
           AND R.POST_DATE >= TO_DATE(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'))
           AND R.POST_DATE <= TO_DATE(SYSDATE)
           AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN
               (101, 102, 103, 111, 121, 131, 132, 133, 141, 151, 161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 171, 183, 191, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227)
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
           AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN
               ('Pacote de Dados', 'Sem Projeção', 'SVA Fixo')
        
        
        
        
        
        
         GROUP BY R.POST_DATE,
                  SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                  P.DESCRIPTION,
                  TO_CHAR(R.POST_DATE,
                          'DD MON YY',
                          'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=PORTUGUESE'),
                  TO_CHAR(R.POST_DATE,
                          'DD-MON-YYYY',
                          'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=PORTUGUESE'),
                  GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC,
                  GD.DESCRIPTION,
                  L.COD_IBGE,
                  GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY,
                  dwadm.f_regional_franquia(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
                                            DECODE(R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION,
                                                   'NÃO CLASSIFICADO',
                                                   'Não Classificado',
                                                   R.RESULT_CENTER_REGION),
                                            L.FLG_FNQ,
                                            L.FLG_AUTHORIZATION_AREA,
                                            L.COD_IBGE),
                  R.CANCELLATION_TYPE,
                  L.NAME,
                  GD.DSC_LNH_NGC, 
                  T.DESCRIPTION,
                  TEC.COD_TCN_BL)
 GROUP BY ANO_MES,
          DATA_REF,
          SEGMENTO,
          REGIONAL,
          LOCALIDADE,
          COD_IBGE,
          TECNOLOGIA,
          GRUPO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_DEMANDA,
          PRODUTO_CONV_DEMANDA

nodes.label: SQL
nodes.query:
SELECT R.POST_DATE MES_REF
,R.CUSTOMER_KEY AS CUSTOMER_KEY
,C.NAME               AS CLIENTE   
,P.DESCRIPTION        AS PRODUTO
,GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC   AS LINHA_NEGOCIO
,GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY||' - '||GD.DESCRIPTION  AS PRODUTO_DEMANDA
,CASE WHEN r.cancellation_type = 'CANCELAMENTO'
               THEN NVL(SUM(R.Quantity),0) ELSE 0
        END CANCELAMENTO
 
  FROM DWADM.IND_CHURN_DAILY_DET           R,
       DWADM.D_DEMAND_PRODUCT              GD,
       DWADM.D_CUSTOMER_SEGMENT            SEG,
       DWADM.D_PRODUCT                     P,
       DWADM.D_CUSTOMER C

  WHERE GD.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY = R.DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY
    AND R.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY = SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT_KEY
    AND P.PRODUCT_KEY = R.PRODUCT_KEY
    AND R.CUSTOMER_KEY = C.CUSTOMER_KEY
    AND GD.RECORD_STATUS = 1
    AND P.RECORD_STATUS = 1
    AND SEG.RECORD_STATUS = 1
    AND C.RECORD_STATUS = 1
  AND R.POST_DATE >= TO_DATE('01/06/2023', 'DD/MM/YYYY')
  AND GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY IN 
  (101,102,103,111,121,131,132,133,141,151,161,162,163,164,165,166,171,183,191,211,212,213,214,215,216,221,222,223,224,225,226,227,231,232,233)
  AND GD.DESCRIPTION IS NOT NULL
  AND GD.DESCRIPTION NOT IN ('Pacote de Dados','Sem Projeção','SVA Fixo')
  AND UPPER(SEG.CUSTOMER_SEGMENT) = 'CORPORATIVO'
  AND GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC IN ( '160 TIC TI','230 TIC Dados')

 
GROUP BY R.POST_DATE 
,R.CUSTOMER_KEY
,C.NAME
,P.DESCRIPTION
,GD.DSC_IDT_LNH_NGC
, GD.SRC_DEMAND_PRODUCT_KEY||' - '||GD.DESCRIPTION 
,r.cancellation_type
